{"tid":407913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【零人生意義】極垃圾 極迷茫","createTime":"2017-09-20T20:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T12:47:37.000Z","uid":135174,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5ac6c34d6290df31eac7b9267fb69c0b20cad2dd","tid":407913,"uid":135174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T20:42:00.000Z","msg":"垃圾人生 <br />\n為左两老而讀大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己完全唔想讀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有得走堂就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇得走既堂就訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全唔知做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打算等畢左業搵工 <br />\n除咗生活費 其他全部比曬做家用<br />\n盡力比佢地過好生活 報答22年養育之恩<br />\n等佢地死左 賣左層樓 到時想點就點 <br />\n鳩hea 去旅行 用曬啲錢就求其死左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實好唔鐘意有負擔 做決定要思前想後<br />\n唔單只要對自己負責 仲要諗埋屋企人<br />\n所以寧願想自己孤身一個 想做乜就做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n單純係連登發表下意見<br />\n希望有人回 唔介意既就講下自己人生意義<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :樓主係垃圾 廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :樓主係垃圾 廢青 不過自己都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6bcf1377186cd52e3f1c0d7ef1875dea2ed400b","tid":407913,"uid":135174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T20:47:58.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b630986729cbd919de8a172cec818fc6e690c33","tid":407913,"uid":83033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T20:49:50.000Z","msg":"點解咁似我既 只係讀大學唔係為屋企 係想玩得耐啲玩得多啲 知道遲啲返工無得再玩 所以大學玩盡佢 只求畢業 不求成績 <br />\n垃圾係自己定義 唔應該比其他人去定義自己<br />\n<br />\nSorry認真左 對唔住 樓主係垃圾 我都係"},{"pid":"2d71368bfb